Description: A departure from what is normal, usual, or expected, typically an unwelcome one.
Well-meaning and kindly; showing goodwill and a desire to help others.
A harsh, discordant mixture of sounds; a chaotic and jarring noise.
Having or showing care and conscientiousness in one's work or duties; industrious.
Cheerful and full of energy; overflowing with enthusiasm.
Attempting to avoid notice or attention, typically because of guilt or a belief that discovery would lead to trouble.
Enjoying the company of others; sociable and outgoing.
A lengthy and aggressive speech; a passionate verbal attack.
Too great or extreme to be expressed in words; indescribable.
The fact of two things being seen or placed close together for contrasting effect.
